closeOut.Rd

Document Processing Time and Other Session Time

closeOut(timeProcess = TRUE, contInfo = TRUE, sessInfo = TRUE)

Arguments

timeProcess

Processing time
contInfo

Contact information
sessInfo

Session information

Value

Reports out processing time, contact information and session information
